<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.190716>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Map showing the known distribution of Chiasmocleis devriesi at the Amazon Conservatory for Tropical Studies (ACTS) Field Station (indicated by star). Color shows elevation (white = below 200 m; light gray = 200 – 500 m; dark gray = above 500 m)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/190716/files/figure.png" ;
